::'''Gouteng:''' By the mercy of Sanctus Medicus! If I'm not mistaken, you must be (Trailblazer), right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why does everybody in this hellhole seem to know who I am?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502080003-->
:::'''Gouteng:''' That's to be expected. Everyone knows everyone in The Shackling Prison, so word travels fast around here.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You know me? I didn't throw you in there, did I?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502080005-->
:::'''Gouteng:''' I wish! Now that'd have been something to boast about. Everyone knows everyone in The Shackling Prison, so word travels fast around here.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502080006-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502080006-->
::'''Gouteng:''' You probably don't know who I am. Let me introduce myself. I'm a former disciple of Sanctus Medicus and the current Chief Technical R&D Officer of the Arma Correctional Group.
::'''Gouteng:''' I'm usually busy developing new products for Arma, but I also sell medicines in a personal capacity. If you're ever in need of medicine, don't hesitate to come to me!
::'''Gouteng:''' And before I forget, the Correctional Group doesn't take monetary payments, only Trick Snacks.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are your medicines licit?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502080010-->
:::'''Gouteng:''' Don't you find this place a little too out of the way to travel to just for licit medicines?
:::'''Gouteng:''' That said, you needn't worry. My goods are absolutely safe for consumption! Madam Chiyi would never greenlight my research in here otherwise.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How dare you covet my Trick Snacks!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502080013-->
:::'''Gouteng:''' Those are just boring old snacks to you, but I'll have you know that they're no different from money to us! I also know that you can synthesize thousands of Trick Snacks with a flick of your wrist... In other words, you hold the reins of The Shackling Prison's entire financial system!
:::'''Gouteng:''' Think of all the profits you could be making if you leveraged that!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502080015-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502080015-->
::'''Gouteng:''' So, how about buying something and supporting the Correctional Group?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502080002: Config/Level/Mission/5020800/Act/Act502080002.json-->
